{"id": "art-4881", "label": "Art. 4881", "title": "Art. 4881: Introducerea contestaţiei", "slug": "art-4881", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1757570141\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1334\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1757570141\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 488<sup>1</sup>:\nIntroducerea contesta&#355;iei </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_192992986\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1333\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_192992986\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Dac&#259; activitatea de urm&#259;rire penal&#259; sau\nde judecat&#259; nu se îndepline&#351;te într-o durat&#259; rezonabil&#259;, se\npoate face contesta&#355;ie, solicitându-se accelerarea procedurii.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1351329103\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1332\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1351329103\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Contesta&#355;ia poate fi introdus&#259; de c&#259;tre\nsuspect, inculpat, persoana v&#259;t&#259;mat&#259;, partea civil&#259; &#351;i\npartea responsabil&#259; civilmente. În cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii,\ncontesta&#355;ia poate fi introdus&#259; &#351;i de c&#259;tre procuror.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_351440058\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1331\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_351440058\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Contesta&#355;ia\npoate fi formulat&#259; dup&#259; cum urmeaz&#259;:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1337524235\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1330\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1337524235\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)dup&#259; cel pu&#355;in un an de la începerea\nurm&#259;ririi penale, pentru cauzele aflate în cursul urm&#259;ririi penale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_674024057\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1329\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_674024057\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)dup&#259; cel pu&#355;in un an de la trimiterea în\njudecat&#259;, pentru cauzele aflate în cursul judec&#259;&#355;ii în\nprim&#259; instan&#355;&#259;;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_162280733\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1328\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_162280733\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)dup&#259; cel pu&#355;in 6 luni de la sesizarea\ninstan&#355;ei cu o cale de atac, pentru cauzele aflate în c&#259;ile de atac\nordinare sau extraordinare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_776916918\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1327\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_776916918\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Contesta&#355;ia poate fi retras&#259; oricând pân&#259;\nla solu&#355;ionarea acesteia. Contesta&#355;ia nu mai poate fi reiterat&#259;\nîn cadrul aceleia&#351;i faze procesuale în care a fost retras&#259;.</span></p>"}